          <figure>
            八年就这么过去了。说起当年事，依旧泪如倾。 (<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27784480/">查看原文</a>)

            <div class="blockquote-extra">
              <div class='blockquote-meta'>
                <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63282586/" class="author-avatar">
                  <img width="20" height="20" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u63282586-18.jpg">
                </a>
                <a class="author-name" href="https://www.douban.com/people/63282586/">西樵山日落</a>
                  <span>5赞</span>
                <datetime>2013-07-26 18:06:05</datetime>
